Class Expense.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cmput301.cs.project.models.Expense.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    Expense

    public static final class Expense.Builder
extends java.lang.Object
    Use this class to obtain instances of Expense.

    Creating an Expense: 

     Expense expense = new Expense.Builder()
                       .amount(BigDecimal.TEN)
                       .currencyUnit(CurrencyUnit.CAD)
                       …
                       .build();

    Editing an Expense: 

     Expense oldExpense = …;
 Expense expense = oldExpense.edit()
                             .amount(BigDecimal.TEN)
                             .currencyUnit(CurrencyUnit.CAD)
                             …
                             .build();
